<li id="cite_note-6">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-6">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite id="CITEREFAnik_Sauvé2013" class="citation web cs1">Anik Sauvé (6 December 2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.justice.gc.ca/eng/rp-pr/csj-sjc/franc/new-bul/12/2.html">"Justice in Official Languages - Newsletter No 12 June 2015"</a>. <i>justice.gc.ca</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">25 June</span> 2019</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=justice.gc.ca&amp;rft.atitle=Justice+in+Official+Languages+-+Newsletter+No+12+June+2015&amp;rft.date=2013-12-06&amp;rft.au=Anik+Sauv%C3%A9&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gc.ca%2Feng%2Frp-pr%2Fcsj-sjc%2Ffranc%2Fnew-bul%2F12%2F2.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALinda+Cardinal" class="Z3988"></span></span>
